{"tid":1727077,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"習近平：「建設一支聽黨指揮....聽黨指揮是靈魂，決定軍隊建設的政治方向。」","createTime":"2019-11-16T10:22:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-17T09:38:57.000Z","uid":155431,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8200e057201290ebfb1383eab2e569dcb74bac7d","tid":1727077,"uid":155431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:22:49.000Z","msg":"2013年3月，習近平在第十二屆全國人民代表大會第一次會議解放軍代表團全體會議上發表講話指出，「建設一支聽黨指揮、能打勝仗、作風優良的人民軍隊，是黨在新形勢下的強軍目標。聽黨指揮是靈魂，決定軍隊建設的政治方向；能打勝仗是核心，反映軍隊的根本職能和軍隊建設的根本指向；作風優良是保證，關係軍隊的性質、宗旨、本色。」<br />\n<br />\n簡單解釋：<br />\n<br />\n軍隊任何行動都是聽黨指揮<br />\n<br />\n而不存在任何「自發」行動<br />\n<br />\n即是 ：<br />\n<br />\n解放軍出營執石仔 &lt;- 背後由黨指揮<br />\n<br />\n無限引申......"},{"pid":"4f5d37017d3d50949fbd98f5f00c6dbbc640a012","tid":1727077,"uid":155431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:24:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64bfe3ff8aaa50bc4953110939243638ffac3d7d","tid":1727077,"uid":120541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:25:54.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">熱烈恭賀鄧炳強登基前已能指揮解放軍出動</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"cb5dcf6f2b0f59e1e2b0ed916f79c5ff87b4d672","tid":1727077,"uid":155431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"64bfe3ff8aaa50bc4953110939243638ffac3d7d","tid":1727077,"uid":120541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:25:54.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">熱烈恭賀鄧炳強登基前已能指揮解放軍出動</span></span></strong>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:31:57.000Z","msg":"解放軍is watching you"},{"pid":"72ed288435e993d42f5256aaa082ad03b85f5828","tid":1727077,"uid":155431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T13:32:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b7062995c78134dee0aba856909ca8e39174854","tid":1727